profile: For over 40 years, we have helped Ontario homeowners and builders build safer, more energy-efficient and sustainable communities. With a broad range of products and services, we are your insulation experts for existing home renovation upgrades and new residential home construction—satisfaction guaranteed. Proudly serving all of Southern Ontario, we are Ontario's largest insulation company and are Energy Star and Foam Masters™ certified. Get in touch for a Free In-Home Assessment—contact us today to learn more.

profile:
TRI COUNTY INSPECTION is committed to being a partner with your real estate needs, by doing all that we can to provide detailed information to assist you in your real estate choice.

Residential Inspections
Providing Home Inspections for Buyers and Sellers as we outline all the major systems within the home. We also use the latest software in home inspection.  Fully meeting the requirements of the Ontario Association of Home Inspectors.  If you have any questions, simply reach out.

New Home Inspections
Also helping the "NEW" home Buyer with one or more of the inspections in working with Tarion Warranty and Your Builder.  The PDI, 30 day, 1 year, 2 year, through to 7 years. Through this service offering, you can count on us to guide you in every step of the process.

Infrared Thermography Inspections
Tri County Inspections wants to help you with the most information we can.  Having a look, as they say, behind the walls is a great tool to add to your Home Inspection.

That's not all.....We can take care of your SEPTIC INSPECTION and your WETT INSPECTION needs!!!

-Septic Inspections

profile:
We know what it takes to provide top-quality service and continuously exceed customer expectations. Our business is based on a professional, friendly, and timely yet thorough home inspection.

We take pride in our personal approach. Our inspection team includes a master inspector, a support inspector and a licensed and certified Heating and Air Conditioning Technician. Our team approach streamlines the inspection process and provides specialized expertise.

The home inspection includes a walk-through with the master inspector so that you see everything that we see during the inspection. A written narrative report is provided within 24 hours and provides all the details you need to make your final decision on the purchase of your home.
